{"tid":2291640,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞大敗後更衣室群毆 傳J洛做帶頭大哥","createTime":"2020-11-19T02:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T10:14:43.000Z","uid":343520,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7a9208e99f1b2ee7ed0cc260dc3f7ff5d22d01","tid":2291640,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】哥倫比亞球星占士洛迪古斯被指在更衣室帶頭進行打鬥。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞周二在世界盃外爆冷作客1:6不敵厄瓜多爾，哥倫比亞記者靴南迪斯透露賽後球隊在更衣室出現集體毆鬥，「兩幫人互相毆打，甚至有人負責帶頭。」隨後電台節目《Language Luciernage》更指出愛華頓球星占士洛迪古斯和般尼茅夫中場謝法臣拿馬，正正是兩幫人的帶頭大哥。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，哥倫比亞賽後氣氛十分火爆，教練基羅斯向球員表示如果責任在他，並透露已經向足總提出辭職，有消息指足總將接受他的呈辭。<br />\n<br />\n靴南迪斯則表示慘敗主因不在教練，而是球員内部的分裂：「球員問題大得多，沒有人出來安撫隊友，卻演變成集體衝突！」哥軍目前在外圍賽4戰得4分排第7，自然不理想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oCKkvN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oCKkvN.jpg&h=12b85506&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c08d11691d91dd592d798925e28c6336520c4e39","tid":2291640,"uid":241543,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"打下交姐"},{"pid":"b47a1b28ae635da4e097a57f4699f1b1497cd0eb","tid":2291640,"uid":17619,"like":426,"dislike":0,"score":426,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"入黎為左睇往死裏打潮文"},{"pid":"c14e78e278023bbc7ddec12d8ab27b5679184dc3","tid":2291640,"uid":212458,"like":252,"dislike":0,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"仲以為係往死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e84bcd432d0d81a5a9c87999ee52fabd67634a","tid":2291640,"uid":6366,"like":128,"dislike":0,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"無往死裏打係咪姐係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1257507f21b469f0291c2bdbb38b3e42726460f","tid":2291640,"uid":68,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"以為係往死裏打"},{"pid":"03aa98d865b0ed24bb7bf1d42e4e4448005dbabe","tid":2291640,"uid":14075,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:51:25.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗，南美區外圍賽求奇踢都出到線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0a33a38720f634dfece53258231a943c8104dd","tid":2291640,"uid":294121,"like":19,"dislike":16,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"皇馬同拜仁都唔要佢<br />\n係愛華頓踢左幾場炒下游以為自己上位<br />\n話咁快打回原型"},{"pid":"aaad0ef16f356be34733ff6fd3af3e208e0283f3","tid":2291640,"uid":59639,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:54:56.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72fd683e7ae315598b0523a1621262479f013f4","tid":2291640,"uid":8000,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"睇到一半睇一睇個user名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed4d90dd59d72ec60e2be511f86047adcfb372e","tid":2291640,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c72fd683e7ae315598b0523a1621262479f013f4","tid":2291640,"uid":8000,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:55:46.000Z","msg":"睇到一半睇一睇個user名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"怎麼了？"},{"pid":"924c3aaba395e1f9a77d961587307cbf1c18b960","tid":2291640,"uid":271513,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:58:09.000Z","msg":"屌 唔係潮文來？！"},{"pid":"43e5653adf128d07428709af82e46de409aa9634","tid":2291640,"uid":99700,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"瘋了 瘋了 都已經瘋了"},{"pid":"41b77d2db6c7f72eed06d141a4eaf08b504e193b","tid":2291640,"uid":3747,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"瘋了瘋了"},{"pid":"a823b916236cf48c76e65219b85946cd5c8d5f41","tid":2291640,"uid":53000,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"世界盃最佳金球球員，明天我們就要回家了"},{"pid":"5e1c25dbed064de73041522aa4281beb8ae890db","tid":2291640,"uid":58841,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:03:21.000Z","msg":"最佳球星，明天我們要回家了"},{"pid":"c497c49eff2a6d7ea8a7a7d3b5f0e3369adc9955","tid":2291640,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"仲以為有潮文睇"},{"pid":"acf9bbca43c706c26998283faa254c65c5e0c972","tid":2291640,"uid":111425,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"你想像不到 當時有十多個人沖上去圍毆J洛"},{"pid":"502f5df376b78aa05fd98a6c039946a3b9f4c2d2","tid":2291640,"uid":43557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"呢次究竟係堅野定潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66686701124ab9acbcf1022b017ecf03f6d56c7f","tid":2291640,"uid":196222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"入黎都係想睇荷蘭三棍潮文"},{"pid":"31c8540deb1b02e113044fcff3aa512c2ace854d","tid":2291640,"uid":172389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"竟然係堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係往死裏打"},{"pid":"bb5251c6c64a498541e860e7819fae6fc735cc0b","tid":2291640,"uid":14983,"like":228,"dislike":1,"score":227,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞隊長占士洛迪古斯在接受哥倫比亞足球報訪問中，炮轟謝法臣拿馬和古亞達度等人，稱他們就是哥倫比亞更衣室的毒瘤。<br />\n<br />\n占士談到：「如果你作為球隊隊長，你本應該感到高興因為這是一種榮譽，你可以帶領你的球隊不斷前進，你就是球隊領袖，但是我從來沒有享受過這樣的待遇，球隊有太多超級球星他們踢球都是以我為主，更衣室經常發生矛盾，開始我還試著去阻止，後來他們直接叫我閉嘴，我根本感覺不到自己就是隊長。」<br />\n<br />\n占士:「在球隊古亞達度常常痛罵一些年輕球員，這在正常不過了，不過也有球員被激怒的時候，記得在一場熱身賽中場休息的時候，古亞達度上半場踢得很不自在，回到更衣室用水瓶怒砸一位才進國家隊的球員，當時很多隊友都已經無法容忍古亞達度的所作所為，在加上那些常被他欺辱的球員無法阻止一幕發生了，至少有10人群毆了古亞達度，你可以想像被10人群毆的滋味，在一旁的奧斯賓拿更是拍手叫好，不停大喊：『給我打，把他往死裡打！』當時梅利奧、謝法臣拿馬這兩位大佬並沒有參與這次毆鬥，他們也沒有阻止好像一切與他兩無關。」<br />\n<br />\n占士：「當發生那件事情後，古亞達度的更衣櫃多了一根鐵棍，我想他是用來防身吧，在2022年世界盃外圍賽古亞達度正是用這根鐵棍報復了奧斯賓拿，在對陣厄瓜多爾比賽結束後，全隊回到更衣室，奧斯賓拿諷刺性說道：『般尼茅夫最佳球員，明天我們就要回家了。』」<br />\n<br />\n「謝法臣拿馬臉色僵硬但並沒有回應什麼，只是默默的走出更衣室，這不像謝法臣拿馬的性格，果然在謝法臣拿馬再次回到更衣室的時候手裡握著一根木棍，在奧斯賓拿毫無防備的情況一棍打下，奧斯賓拿挨那一下著實不輕，趴在地上痛苦的抬頭才看到是打他那人正是謝法臣拿馬，不等奧斯賓拿起身，謝法臣拿馬又是一頓亂棍爆打，奧斯賓拿在地上滿地打滾不停求饒，在一旁的古亞達度可不會放過這樣的機會不斷說道：『謝法臣拿馬，打狗，用力打，往死裡給我打，打狗怎能少了我。 』」<br />\n<br />\n「古亞達度的防身鐵棍終於派上了用場，可惜一棍下去奧斯賓拿就昏死了過去，打的興起的謝法臣拿馬怒了，朝著古亞達度吼道：『這下還還怎麼打，你該滾一邊去！』古亞達度也不甘示弱：『你再說一遍，有種你重複一遍！』謝法臣拿馬沒有在回應古亞達度什麼，如果古亞達度手上沒有鐵棍那麼他們肯定會打起來。當時我身邊的隊醫嘴裡不停的說：『瘋了，瘋了，都已經瘋了。』」"},{"pid":"b608011c75dbe47b227d393d8ca54b069e2d46a4","tid":2291640,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"占士唔似咁燥咁愛國架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前國家隊隊醫先屌過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84e9bc891cc26500693dc784871079ba3061f35","tid":2291640,"uid":308251,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f0a33a38720f634dfece53258231a943c8104dd","tid":2291640,"uid":294121,"like":19,"dislike":16,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"皇馬同拜仁都唔要佢<br />\n係愛華頓踢左幾場炒下游以為自己上位<br />\n話咁快打回原型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"真，棄將吹到幾勁幾勁，成地精"},{"pid":"4e1a21d0e1e806ddb9af2570e442a4bfb20795ab","tid":2291640,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"對厄瓜都輸1:6<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dfc5c6237984c5e7946d730a64a3ef7452de53","tid":2291640,"uid":14103,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"bb5251c6c64a498541e860e7819fae6fc735cc0b","tid":2291640,"uid":14983,"li